$Id: INSTALL 46 2008-10-13 06:13:53Z dot $

apctl : alsaplayer controll command set.

1. required libraries

    apctl required libalsaplayer(alsaplayer development libraries).
    so, install libalsaplayer before make apctl.

    If debian user, execute following command for install libalsaplayer.

        # aptitude install libalsaplayer-dev

2. make

    # make

3. install

    # make install
